From: Ken Zhu <guigenz@codeaurora.org>
Date: Wed, 13 May 2020 17:14:25 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] odhcpd: disable odhcpd by default

odhcpd impact performance, disable it by default.

Change-Id: Ib81c182cb6e4802abae1994d371a29b8c50a2de6
Signed-off-by: Ken Zhu <guigenz@codeaurora.org>
---
 package/network/services/odhcpd/files/odhcpd.defaults | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/package/network/services/odhcpd/files/odhcpd.defaults b/package/network/services/odhcpd/files/odhcpd.defaults
index 1350636ba430..a2fb8dca0e02 100644
--- a/package/network/services/odhcpd/files/odhcpd.defaults
+++ b/package/network/services/odhcpd/files/odhcpd.defaults
@@ -50,3 +50,8 @@ add_list dhcp.lan.ra_flags=managed-config
 add_list dhcp.lan.ra_flags=other-config
 commit dhcp
 EOF
+
+/etc/init.d/odhcpd enabled && {
+	/etc/init.d/odhcpd stop
+	/etc/init.d/odhcpd disable
+}
